# Design Patterns - Faith Generation App

## Design Philosophy

The Faith Generation App follows the **faithgeneration.com** website design: a **minimal black, white, and grey** palette. The design should feel:

- **Minimal**: Black, white, and grey only – no colored accents (except error red)
- **Clean**: High contrast, clear typography hierarchy
- **Professional**: Aligned with the ministry’s website aesthetic
- **Readable**: Neutral backgrounds with proper text contrast

## Faith Generation Color Palette

Colors match [faithgeneration.com](https://faithgeneration.com/).

### Light Mode

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `pageBg` | `#FFFFFF` | Page background |
| `cardBg` | `#FAFAFA` | Card background |
| `cardBorder` | `#E5E5E5` | Borders, dividers |
| `textPrimary` | `#000000` | Headings, primary text |
| `textSecondary` | `#525252` | Body, labels |
| `textTertiary` | `#737373` | Placeholders, muted text |
| `buttonPrimary` | `#171717` | Primary CTAs |
| `buttonPrimaryContrast` | `#FFFFFF` | Text on primary buttons |
| `avatarPrimary` | `#E5E5E5` | Icon/avatar backgrounds |

### Dark Mode

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `pageBg` | `#0a0a0a` | Page background |
| `cardBg` | `#171717` | Card background |
| `cardBorder` | `#262626` | Borders, dividers |
| `textPrimary` | `#FAFAFA` | Headings, primary text |
| `textSecondary` | `#a3a3a3` | Body, labels |
| `textTertiary` | `#737373` | Placeholders, muted text |
| `buttonPrimary` | `#FAFAFA` | Primary CTAs |
| `buttonPrimaryContrast` | `#171717` | Text on primary buttons |
| `avatarPrimary` | `#262626` | Icon/avatar backgrounds |

### Semantic (both modes)

- `buttonDecline` / `badgeError`: Red for errors
- `badgeSuccess`: Green for success
- `badgeWarning`: Amber for warnings

## Theme System

### useTheme Hook

Always use the centralized `useTheme` hook instead of hardcoded colors:

```typescript
import { useTheme } from "@/hooks/useTheme";

function MyComponent() {
  const theme = useTheme();

  return (
    <Box style={{ backgroundColor: theme.pageBg }}>
      <Text style={{ color: theme.textPrimary }}>Hello</Text>
      <Button style={{ backgroundColor: theme.buttonPrimary }}>
        <ButtonText style={{ color: theme.buttonPrimaryContrast }}>Submit</ButtonText>
      </Button>
    </Box>
  );
}
```

### Theme Interface

- `pageBg`, `cardBg`, `cardBorder` – backgrounds and borders
- `textPrimary`, `textSecondary`, `textTertiary` – typography
- `buttonPrimary`, `buttonPrimaryContrast` – primary CTAs (use `buttonPrimaryContrast` for text on primary buttons)
- `buttonAccept`, `buttonDecline` – semantic actions
- `avatarPrimary`, `badgeSuccess`, `badgeError`, `badgeWarning`, `badgeInfo` – component backgrounds
- `isDark` – boolean for dark mode logic

### Gluestack Config

`components/ui/gluestack-ui-provider/config.ts` uses a greyscale primary palette (black in light, white in dark). GluestackUIProvider follows system color scheme: `mode={colorScheme ?? 'light'}`.

## Typography

### Brand Label

- "Faith Generation" / "Faith Generation Bijbelschool": `text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest`, `theme.textSecondary`

### Headings

- Primary: `text-2xl` or `text-3xl`, `font-bold`, `theme.textPrimary`
- Secondary: `text-base`, `theme.textSecondary`, `lineHeight: 22–24`

### Body

- `text-base`, `theme.textPrimary` or `theme.textSecondary`
- `lineHeight: 24` for readability

## Cards & Surfaces

- Background: `theme.cardBg`
- Border: `theme.cardBorder`
- Shadow (light): `shadowOpacity: 0.06`, `shadowRadius: 16`
- Shadow (dark): `shadowOpacity: 0.25`, `shadowRadius: 16`
- Corners: `rounded-2xl` for large cards, `rounded-xl` for smaller
- Use `theme.isDark` when shadow/border behavior differs by mode

## Buttons

### Primary

- Background: `theme.buttonPrimary`
- Text: `theme.buttonPrimaryContrast` (never hardcode white/black)
- Size: `h-14` for main CTAs
- Corners: `rounded-2xl`

### Secondary / Ghost

- Background: `transparent`
- Border: `theme.textTertiary` or `theme.textSecondary`
- Text: `theme.textSecondary`

### Touch Feedback

- `TouchableOpacity` with `activeOpacity={0.7}`

## Form Inputs

- Background: `theme.cardBg` (dark) or `#ffffff` (light)
- Border: `theme.cardBorder` or `#e5e7eb` (light)
- Focus/error: `theme.buttonPrimary` (focus), `theme.buttonDecline` (error)
- Labels: `theme.textSecondary`
- Placeholders: `theme.textTertiary`

## Spacing & Layout

- Page padding: `px-6`, `pt-6`, `pb-8`
- Between sections: `gap-6`
- Between related items: `gap-3` or `gap-4`
- Card internal: `p-5` or `p-8`

## LoadingScreen

- Use `LoadingScreen` from `@/components/ui/LoadingScreen` for full-screen loading
- Component uses `theme.pageBg`, `theme.buttonPrimary`, `theme.textSecondary` – no hardcoded colors

## Don'ts

- Don’t add purple, gold, blue, or other accent colors – stick to black/white/grey (plus red for errors)
- Don’t hardcode hex values – use `theme.*` tokens
- Don’t use `#ffffff` or `#000000` directly where theme tokens exist
- Don’t assume button text color – use `buttonPrimaryContrast` on primary buttons

## Do's

- Use `useTheme()` in all UI components
- Use `theme.isDark` instead of comparing `pageBg` to hex values
- Follow system color scheme (light/dark)
- Keep Faith Generation branding consistent with faithgeneration.com
